summary: An ordinance relating to the Water Dept. and authorizing the sale and remvoal of alder timber, other hardwood forest materials and of certain additional materials incidental to thinning and salvage from City-owned lands in Townships 22 & 23 North, Range 7 East, W.M. and Townships 21, 22 & 23 North, Range 8 East, W.M. and Township 22 North, Range 9 East, W.M. in the Cedar River Watershed under contract with Masao Nakaso.
